#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:2
msgid "安全开发"
msgstr "Secure Development"

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Introduction"

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:6
msgid ""
"安全开发生命周期（Security Development "
"Lifecycle，SDL）是微软提出的从安全的角度来指导软件开发过程的管理模式。用于帮助开发人员构建更安全的软件、解决安全合规要求，并降低开发成本。"
msgstr "The Security Development Lifecycle (SDL) is a management model proposed by Microsoft to guide the software development process from a security perspective. It helps developers build more secure software, address security compliance requirements, and reduce development costs."

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:9
msgid "步骤"
msgstr "Steps"

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:12
msgid "阶段1：培训"
msgstr "Phase 1: Training"

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:13
msgid "开发团队的所有成员都必须接受适当的安全培训，了解相关的安全知识。培训对象包括开发人员、测试人员、项目经理、产品经理等。"
msgstr "All members of the development team must receive appropriate security training and understand relevant security knowledge. Training targets include developers, testers, project managers, product managers, and others."

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:16
msgid "阶段2：确定安全需求"
msgstr "Phase 2: Define Security Requirements"

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:17
msgid "在项目确立之前，需要提前确定安全方面的需求，确定项目的计划时间，尽可能避免安全引起的需求变更。"
msgstr "Before a project is established, security requirements and the project schedule should be defined in advance to avoid requirement changes caused by security issues as much as possible."

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:20
msgid "阶段3：设计"
msgstr "Phase 3: Design"

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:21
msgid "在设计阶段确定安全的最低可接受级别。考虑项目涉及到哪些攻击面、是否能减小攻击面。"
msgstr "During the design phase, determine the minimum acceptable security level. Consider which attack surfaces the project involves and whether those attack surfaces can be reduced."

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:23
msgid "对项目进行威胁建模，明确可能来自的攻击有哪些方面，并考虑项目哪些部分需要进行渗透测试。"
msgstr "Perform threat modeling for the project, identify the possible sources and types of attacks, and consider which parts of the project require penetration testing."

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:26
msgid "阶段4：实现"
msgstr "Phase 4: Implementation"

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:27
msgid "实现阶段主要涉及到工具、不安全的函数、静态分析等方面。"
msgstr "The implementation phase mainly involves tools, unsafe functions, static analysis, and related areas."

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:29
msgid "工具方面主要考虑到开发团队使用的编辑器、链接器等相关工具可能会涉及一些安全相关的问题，因此在使用工具的版本上，需要提前与安全团队进行沟通。"
msgstr "For tools, consider that editors, linkers, and other tools used by the development team may involve security-related issues. Therefore, tool versions should be discussed with the security team in advance."

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:31
msgid "函数方面主要考虑到许多常用函数可能存在安全隐患，应当禁用不安全的函数和API，使用安全团队推荐的函数。"
msgstr "For functions, consider that many commonly used functions may have security risks. Unsafe functions and APIs should be disabled, and functions recommended by the security team should be used."

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:33
msgid "代码静态分析可以由相关工具辅助完成，其结果与人工分析相结合。"
msgstr "Static code analysis can be assisted by relevant tools, and its results should be combined with manual analysis."

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:36
msgid "阶段5：验证"
msgstr "Phase 5: Verification"

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:37
msgid "验证阶段涉及到动态程序分析和攻击面再审计。动态分析对静态分析进行补充，常用的方式是模糊测试、渗透测试。模糊测试通过向应用程序引入特定格式或随机数据查找程序可能的问题。"
msgstr "The verification phase involves dynamic program analysis and attack surface re-auditing. Dynamic analysis complements static analysis; common methods include fuzz testing and penetration testing. Fuzz testing finds potential program issues by introducing specifically formatted or random data into an application."

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:39
msgid "考虑到项目经常会因为需求变更等情况使得最终产品和初期目标不一致，因此需要在项目后期再次对威胁模型和攻击面进行分析和考虑，如果出现问题则进行纠正。"
msgstr "Because requirement changes and similar factors often make the final product differ from the initial goals, the threat model and attack surface need to be analyzed and reviewed again in the later stages of the project. If problems appear, they should be corrected."

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:42
msgid "阶段6：发布"
msgstr "Phase 6: Release"

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:43
msgid "在程序发布后，需要对安全事件进行响应，需要预设好遇到安全问题时的处理方式。"
msgstr "After the program is released, security incidents must be handled, and response procedures for security issues should be predefined."

#: ../../source/defense/sdl.rst:45
msgid "另外如果产品中包含第三方的代码，也需要考虑如何响应因为第三方依赖引入的问题。"
msgstr "In addition, if the product contains third-party code, consider how to respond to issues introduced by third-party dependencies."

